@startuml

title Lookup Party By MSISDN

hide footbox

autonumber

box "Mobile Device" #Light
  actor Alice
  participant "PISP App" as App
end box
box "PISP" #Light
  database Firebase
  participant "PISP Server" as Server
end box
box "Mojaloop" #Light
  participant "Switch" as Mojaloop
end box

Alice -> App: I want to lookup info\nfor this party

rnote right of App #Light 
  ""firebase.firestore()""
  ""  .collection("lookups")""
  ""  .doc("MSISDN/+1-222-222-2222")""
  ""  .get()""
end rnote

App -> Firebase ++: Get a document from the database
return ""200 OK""

opt "Document does not exist"
  rnote right of App #Light 
    ""firebase.firestore()""
    ""  .collection("lookups")""
    ""  .doc("MSISDN/+1-222-222-2222")""
    ""  .set({""
