    ""event(""
    ""  "document.create",""
    ""  "lookups/MSISDN/+1-222-222-2222",""
    ""  <snapshot object>""
    "")""
  end rnote

  Firebase -> Server ++: Notify event for new document
  Firebase <-- Server: ""200 OK""
  deactivate Firebase 

  Server -> Mojaloop ++: ""**GET /parties/MSISDN/+1-222-222-2222**""
